  "id": "api/core/HostBinding",
  "title": "HostBinding",
  "contents": "<article>\n  <div class=\"breadcrumb-container\">\n    <div class=\"breadcrumb\">\n      <script type=\"application/ld+json\">\n        {\n          \"@context\": \"http://schema.org\",\n          \"@type\": \"BreadcrumbList\",\n          \"itemListElement\": [\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 1, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api\", \"name\": \"API\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 2, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core\", \"name\": \"@angular/core\" } },\n            { \"@type\": \"ListItem\", \"position\": 3, \"item\": { \"@id\": \"https://angular.io/api/core/HostBinding\", \"name\": \"HostBinding\" } }\n          ]\n        }\n      </script>\n        <a href=\"/api\">API</a> > <a href=\"api/core\">@angular/core</a>\n    </div>\n    <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L992-L992\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n  </div>\n  <header class=\"api-header\">\n    <h1 id=\"hostbinding\">HostBinding<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostBinding#hostbinding\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h1>\n    <label class=\"api-type-label decorator\">decorator</label>\n  </header>\n  <aio-toc class=\"embedded\"></aio-toc>\n\n  <div class=\"api-body\">\n  <section class=\"short-description\">\n    <p>Decorator that marks a DOM property or an element class, style or attribute as a host-binding\nproperty and supplies configuration metadata. Angular automatically checks host bindings during\nchange detection, and if a binding changes it updates the host element of the directive.</p>\n\n  </section>\n<section class=\"decorator-overview\">\n  <table class=\"is-full-width list-table option-overview\">\n  <thead>\n    <tr><th>Option</th><th>Description</th></tr>\n  </thead>\n  <tbody>\n    <tr class=\"option\">\n      <td>\n        <a class=\"code-anchor\" href=\"api/core/HostBinding#hostPropertyName\">\n          <code>hostPropertyName?</code>\n        </a>\n      </td>\n      <td>\n\n        <p>The DOM property that is bound to a data property.\nThis field also accepts:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>classes, prefixed by <code>class.</code></li>\n<li>styles, prefixed by <code>style.</code></li>\n<li>attributes, prefixed by <code>attr.</code></li>\n</ul>\n\n      </td>\n    </tr>\n  </tbody>\n</table>\n  \n</section>\n\n\n<section class=\"decorator-options\">\n  <h2 id=\"options\">Options<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostBinding#options\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  \n  \n  <a id=\"hostPropertyName\"></a>\n  <table class=\"is-full-width option-table\">\n    <thead>\n      <tr>\n        <th>\n          <div class=\"with-github-links\">\n            <h3 id=\"hostpropertyname\">hostPropertyName<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostBinding#hostpropertyname\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h3>\n            <div class=\"github-links\">\n  <a href=\"https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L977-L984\" aria-label=\"View Source\" title=\"View Source\"><i class=\"material-icons\" aria-hidden=\"true\" role=\"img\">code</i></a>\n</div>\n          </div>\n        </th>\n      </tr>\n    </thead>\n    <tbody>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <p>The DOM property that is bound to a data property.\nThis field also accepts:</p>\n<ul>\n<li>classes, prefixed by <code>class.</code></li>\n<li>styles, prefixed by <code>style.</code></li>\n<li>attributes, prefixed by <code>attr.</code></li>\n</ul>\n\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n      <tr>\n        <td>\n          <code-example language=\"ts\" hidecopy=\"true\" class=\"no-box api-heading\">\n            hostPropertyName?: string\n          </code-example>\n        </td>\n      </tr>\n    </tbody>\n  </table>\n  \n  \n</section>\n\n<section class=\"usage-notes\">\n  <h2 id=\"usage-notes\">Usage notes<a title=\"Link to this heading\" class=\"header-link\" aria-hidden=\"true\" href=\"api/core/HostBinding#usage-notes\"><i class=\"material-icons\">link</i></a></h2>\n  <p>The following example creates a directive that sets the <code>valid</code> and <code>invalid</code>\nclass, a style color, and an id on the DOM element that has an <code><a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a></code> directive on it.</p>\n<code-example language=\"typescript\">\n@<a href=\"api/core/Directive\" class=\"code-anchor\">Directive</a>({selector: '[<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>]'})\nclass NgModelStatus {\n  constructor(public control: <a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">NgModel</a>) {}\n  // class bindings\n  @<a href=\"api/core/HostBinding\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostBinding</a>('class.valid') get valid() { return this.control.valid; }\n  @<a href=\"api/core/HostBinding\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostBinding</a>('class.invalid') get invalid() { return this.control.invalid; }\n\n  // <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a> binding\n  @<a href=\"api/core/HostBinding\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostBinding</a>('style.color') get color() { return this.control.valid ? 'green': 'red'; }\n\n  // <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a> binding also supports a <a href=\"api/animations/style\" class=\"code-anchor\">style</a> unit extension\n  @<a href=\"api/core/HostBinding\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostBinding</a>('style.width.px') @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>() width: number = 500;\n\n  // attribute binding\n  @<a href=\"api/core/HostBinding\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostBinding</a>('attr.aria-required')\n  @<a href=\"api/core/Input\" class=\"code-anchor\">Input</a>() required: boolean = false;\n\n  // property binding\n  @<a href=\"api/core/HostBinding\" class=\"code-anchor\">HostBinding</a>('id') get id() { return this.control.value?.length ? 'odd':  'even'; }\n\n@<a href=\"api/core/Component\" class=\"code-anchor\">Component</a>({\n  selector: 'app',\n  template: `&#x3C;input [(<a href=\"api/forms/NgModel\" class=\"code-anchor\">ngModel</a>)]=\"prop\">`,\n})\nclass App {\n  prop;\n}\n</code-example>\n\n</section></div>\n</article>\n\n<!-- links to this doc:\n - api/animations/trigger\n - api/core\n - guide/add-an-animation\n - guide/animations\n - guide/cheatsheet\n - guide/elements\n - guide/style-precedence\n - guide/styleguide\n - guide/transition-and-triggers\n-->\n<!-- links from this doc:\n - /api\n - api/animations/style\n - api/core\n - api/core/Component\n - api/core/Directive\n - api/core/HostBinding#hostPropertyName\n - api/core/HostBinding#hostbinding\n - api/core/HostBinding#hostpropertyname\n - api/core/HostBinding#options\n - api/core/HostBinding#usage-notes\n - api/core/Input\n - api/forms/NgModel\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L977-L984\n - https://github.com/angular/angular/tree/17.3.12/packages/core/src/metadata/directives.ts#L992-L992\n-->"
